Bad Attitude - A Danish CSS Clan!
------------------------------------------------
This i a new version of the popular map "hoejhus9".
In this version is there a tiny pool and a new bridge.
And some BA logos :D

Enjoy!
------------------------------------------------
Installation:

Put the hoejhus9_bad_attitude_v1.bsp in your map folder
wich is located in C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\frimann\counter-strike source\cstrike
